013package org.apache.juneau.dto.jsonschema;
014
015import java.util.*;
016
017/**
018 * Represents a list of {@link JsonSchema} objects.
019 *
020 * <ul class='seealso'>
021 *    <li class='jp'><a class="doclink" href="package-summary.html#TOC">org.apache.juneau.dto.jsonschema</a>
022
023 * </ul>
024 *
025 * @serial exclude
026 */
027public class JsonSchemaArray extends LinkedList<JsonSchema> {
028
029   private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;
030
031   /**
032    * Default constructor.
033    */
034   public JsonSchemaArray() {}
035
036   /**
037    * Constructor with predefined types to add to this list.
038    *
039    * @param schemas The list of schemas in this array.
040    */
041   public JsonSchemaArray(JsonSchema...schemas) {
042      addAll(schemas);
043   }
044
045   /**
046    * Convenience method for adding one or more {@link JsonSchema} objects to this array.
047    *
048    * @param schemas The {@link JsonSchema} objects to add to this array.
049    * @return This object.
050    */
051   public JsonSchemaArray addAll(JsonSchema...schemas) {
052      Collections.addAll(this, schemas);
053      return this;
054   }
055}
